---
description: Project-level AI coding constraints for this repository.
alwaysApply: true
---

- This repository is frontend-focused.
- Prefer Next.js App Router patterns and existing project conventions.
- Prefer existing shadcn/ui components before custom markup.
- Use Tailwind semantic tokens; avoid hard-coded colors and ad-hoc design tokens.
- Keep diffs small and task-focused.
- Skills live in `.ai/skills/*/SKILL.md` (canonical source); `.cursor/skills/` is a generated junction pointing there.
- Validate changes with the smallest relevant commands first (`pnpm typecheck`, `pnpm check`, `pnpm agile:check`).
